a> ）。近日管理團隊發現情況有所惡化，因此將會加強審視主題內容真確性，並會封鎖多次或惡意散佈假消息的會員。我們亦正準備與從事 fact check 相關的機構合作，減少假資訊於討論區散播，如有任何進展，將會再另行公告。當然，最重要的是希望會員能判別資訊真確性，勿盲目相信或轉發不明來源或未經證實的消息。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4dfa1bfd3a118ea4a42e26137c0287c2c9e0b6f2","tid":2050060,"uid":74339,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:48:32.000Z","msg":"總統言論冇source 拉"},{"pid":"11204f853b25838961d0241f128279afbe16d06e","tid":2050060,"uid":3149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T02:54:35.000Z","msg":"Fake news <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2637e3b8cd96ad379b3aca18b32615607359a61a","tid":2050060,"uid":170987,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T03:18:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kshqDVQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkshqDVQ.gif&h=e6d06aa5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8fada00603c7dd8627ad85a9e897a4a2d2dfd2a","tid":2050060,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T03:29:37.000Z","msg":"子彈最終擊中居民左腿<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係香港D黑警係喵頭射....<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n爆眼~<br />\n爆頭~~ (雖然話係橡膠子彈, 但我估有幾好多單爆左頭無上到頭條A1, 可能手足戴左頭盔, 無咁傷)"},{"pid":"fd5b8225f856bf18a342de0f8354a72c5d38ffbd","tid":2050060,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T03:44:00.000Z","msg":"FAKE NEWS"}]}